### 3. PROVIDER UTILITIES (`@ai-sdk/provider-utils`)

**File:** `/packages/provider-utils/src/index.ts`

Common utilities used by image providers:

| Utility | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `postToApi()` / `postJsonToApi()` / `postFormDataToApi()` | HTTP POST requests with error handling |
| `downloadBlob()` | Download files from URLs with size limits |
