| `parseProviderOptions()` | Validate provider-specific options against schemas |
| `convertImageModelFileToDataUri()` | Convert image files to data URIs |
| `convertToFormData()` | Convert objects to FormData |
| `lazySchema()` | Lazy Zod schema evaluation |
| `zodSchema()` / `jsonSchema()` | Schema type conversions |
| `parseJSON()` | JSON parsing with schema validation |
| `isAbortError()` | Check if error is abort-related |
| `extractResponseHeaders()` | Get headers from Response objects |

